[normal] which means that it is much more amenable to all of t
[normal]hose involved in 
[normal]prescribing
[normal] antibiotics,
[normal] administering antibiotics or caring for patients on antibiotics. That type of approach is extremely welcome, but we must remi
[normal]nd ourselves that it is not a policy;
