[normal]Professor [bold]Lewith[bold]: 
[normal]My background is as a clinician, a GP, so I can add to some of the comments made by Dr Moore and I can certainly expand any that may be relevant to this part of the meeting. As a primary care physician, you a
[normal]re in a very difficult position;
[normal] you are in a one
[normal]&#x2011;
[normal]to
